is by richard kluger  guns germs and steel the fates of human societies by jared diamond  annals of the former world by john mcphee  embracing defeat by john w dower  complete list – – – authority control worldcat identities viaf  lccn n isni     gnd  sudoc  bnf cbj data ndl  retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitledanielyerginoldid categories  birthsthcentury american historiansthcentury american writersstcentury american historiansstcentury american writersalumni of the university of cambridgeamerican economics writersamerican male writersamerican nonfiction environmental writersbeverly hills high school alumniharvard business school facultyjohn f kennedy school of government facultyliving peoplemarshall scholarspeople associated with energypulitzer prize for general nonfiction winnersyale university alumnihidden categories use mdy dates from january articles with hcardswikipedia articles needing factual verification from may all articles with unsourced statementsarticles with unsourced statements from may wikipedia articles with viaf identifierswikipedia articles with lccn identifierswikipedia articles with isni identifierswikipedia articles with gnd identifierswikipedia articles with bnf identifiers navigation menu personal tools not logged intalkcontributionscreate accountlog in namespaces article talk variants views read edit view history more search navigation main pagecontentsfeatured contentcurrent eventsrandom articledonate to wikipediawikipedia store interaction helpabout wikipediacommunity portalrecent changescontact page tools what links hererelated changesupload filespecial pagespermanent linkpage informationwikidata itemcite this page printexport create a bookdownload as pdfprintable version in other projects wikimedia commons languages deutschfrançaisitalianonederlandsnorsk bokmålрусский edit links this page was last edited on  july  at  text is available under the creative commons attributionsharealike license additional terms may apply by u